                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 10044/167.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Leishman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Pera</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-04-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 27, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Leishman says the Sultan has been dethroned, and that his brother, Rechad,
                    who will reign under the name of Mohammed Fifth, has been placed on the
                    throne.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
